text: Ðis sind þara III hida landgemæra to hamstede.

Ærest of suðeweardan fif æceran on<../images/tbar.gif>riþe on þa uuiþigas of þan uuiþigan on heafod stoccas þanan andlang hagan to gæcce lege estewearde þanan andlang hagan on Riscmere þanan to beonat lege þær mercweg ut scet þanan andlang weges on gecceleage þanan andlang uueges to þan forda of þan forda andlang hagan<../images/tbar.gif>eft to fif æceran.
